{"tid":492071,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係不求完美者？","createTime":"2017-12-07T07:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T08:40:38.000Z","uid":26020,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"346452b034e0efa8d921fca5935e834962b5d12f","tid":492071,"uid":26020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T07:07:15.000Z","msg":"例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/145942_66369a50f5bf3cd05cad4a41cc8384e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F145942_66369a50f5bf3cd05cad4a41cc8384e8.jpg&h=1923ff31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不嬲都唔會開曬 <br />\n啲強逼症嘅人成日屌柒我，佢地根本唔明<br />\n仲有我好鐘意缺陷美<br />\n例子<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/150543_8835f785026f93e39d5a5c315c012f8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F150543_8835f785026f93e39d5a5c315c012f8d.jpg&h=e8bef5b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我唔知呢啲叫虎牙定爆牙啦<br />\n但係佢隻牙係最吸引嘅地方<br />\n有冇人係同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0fe94cac0d5f48c3b2a23905eaa39d72941fb92","tid":492071,"uid":26020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T07:10:42.000Z","msg":"仲有楊𠄘琳粒閪墨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/150955_f3dd5f46348502644839bfd01805bb6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F150955_f3dd5f46348502644839bfd01805bb6f.jpg&h=df638c8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"388e4daaf815664099073b9513dd19ed7fd1e223","tid":492071,"uid":26020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T07:46:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9aca2d5fcf147a44b76b90cb5de627ed335b655","tid":492071,"uid":26020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T07:46:29.000Z","msg":"